CLAUDE.md

# ─── Supabase CLI local artifacts ─────────────────────────
supabase/.temp/
supabase/.branches/

# ─── Capacitor iOS native build artifacts (Phase 4c) ──────
# The `ios/` project itself IS committed (generated on the build Mac via
# `npx cap add ios`), but its heavy/derived artifacts are not.
ios/App/Pods/
ios/App/App/public/
ios/App/build/
ios/DerivedData/
ios/.gradle/
*.xcuserstate

# ─── GCP service-account keys — NEVER commit (live credentials) ───
reference/blip-*.json
*.iam.gserviceaccount.com.json
gcp-*-key.json

# ─── Go-live E2E run state — test credentials + Chrome profiles (never commit) ───
.agents/e2e/state/

# ─── Generated poster candidates — scratch output of the m0 pipeline (~200M) ───
assets/m0/cand-*/

# ─── Fastlane generated test report ───
fastlane/report.xml
